data.name: lblDescription.Text
data.value:
With this function it is possible to extract the token of all devices from MiHome. With this token you can use other system to control i.e. your robot vacuum.
There are the following requirements: ● USB-Debugging activated ● Installed Java ● Smartphone connected to the PC
The following steps will start if you press the big button: 1. Creating a backup of the MiHome App -> Confirm on Smartphone and DON'T SET A PASSWORD 2. Extract Backup 3. Extract Token
